quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  26,53,Basi Firiauna ni jwatumisye m’misinda (josope) akusonganganya
  26,54,"(Ŵaŵapitaga nchigombelesya yanti): “Chisimu ŵanganyaŵa (ŵanache ŵa Israila) ali kwene kankutula kannono.”"
  26,55,“Soni chisimu ŵanganyao akutupikasya ntima.”
  26,56,“Soni chisimu uwwe tuli wosope (ŵajinji nambo soni) tuli mesope (tukwalolechesya ŵanganyao kuti akatupatisya ipato iliyose).”
  26,57,Basi Uwwe ni twakopwesye ŵanganyao (ŵanya Afiriauna) m’matimbe ni achitutumule
  26,58,Kwisa soni mu imatiilo yachipanje ni m’malo mwakuchimbichika
  26,59,"Mwele (ni mutwatendele), ni twaitesile kuŵa yawinjilwa ni ŵanache ŵa Israila"
  26,60,Basi ŵanganyao ni ŵakuyiye (ŵanache ŵa Israilao) pakopoka kwa lyuŵa
  26,61,"Basi ndema jagaonegene makuga ganagaŵili (likuga lya Firiauna ni lya Musa), ŵandu ŵa Musa ŵatite: “Chisimu uwwe chitukamulwe.”"
  26,62,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ngwamba! Chisimu Ambuje ŵangu ali none, chanjongolele (yakutenda kuti mpaka tujokoche).”"
  26,63,"Basi ni twan’juwulile Musa (maloŵe ganti): “Putani mbwani ni simbo jenujo.” Ni jagaŵanyiche, upande uliose waliji nti chisawu litumbi lyekulungwa"
  26,64,Ni twaŵandichisye palakwepo ŵaneo (Firiauna ni ŵandu ŵakwe)
  26,65,Ni twan’jokwele Musa ni ŵaŵaliji najo imo wosopeŵene
  26,66,Kaneka ni twamisisye ŵaneo (Firiauna ni ŵandu ŵakwe)
  26,67,Chisimu mu yalakweyi mwana chimanyisyo (cha ukombosi wa Allah). Nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao nganaŵa ŵakulupilila
  26,68,"Soni chisimu Ambuje ŵenu niŵali Ŵamachili gakupunda, Ŵachanasa channope"
  26,69,Soni mwasoomelani ŵanganyao abali ja Ibrahima